Package: mlpackplus
Type: Package
Title: Machine Learning Algorithms Inspired by mlpack
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("mlpackplus", "authors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                   email = "mlpackplus@example.com")
Description: Implements machine learning algorithms inspired by the mlpack C++
    library, using Rcpp and RcppArmadillo for performance-critical code.
    Includes CART decision trees, random forests, alternating matrix
    factorization (NMF), spill-tree KNN search, cross-validation, and
    hyperparameter tuning frameworks.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
