RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.0),
    stats
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
